Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Haig's shuttle diplomacy over Falklands
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wvcw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 18 Apr 1982
Haig admits aiding Britain with intelligence amid shuttle diplomacy between the two warring nations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less